subtitleNullable: Can you classify disasters by images?
descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset contains images for each disaster. Images are placed in folders with disaster name. Images with no damage are also available, for model training purposes. Can you develop a model to classify images into type of disaster?

If you have any suggestions/improvements in the dataset, please feel free to message me.
